{"tid":1725112,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"重整旗鼓 保持初心 查證來源 持續文宣","createTime":"2019-11-15T15:57:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-16T02:51:25.000Z","uid":87582,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"ddae734856450034b7748e7de755be52643cf52c","tid":1725112,"uid":87582,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T15:57:43.000Z","msg":"好撚簡單真係<br />\n依家真係求鳩其出啲野話咩咩咩就信<br />\n唔該做返fact check <br />\n依5個月明明一直做緊<br />\n<br />\n文宣唔好停呀<br />\n要繼續做<br />\n做做做做做<br />\n一黎要澄清我地做嘅野背後嘅原因<br />\n二黎要打國際線<br />\n<br />\n保持返一開始初衷<br />\n兄弟爬山 各自努力<br />\n不分化 不割席 不篤灰<br />\n唔好再理任何分化撚<br />\n我諗做得前線出得多戰場自然有意識知幾時要做啲咩<br />\n同時我相信大家係有智慧 唔會比風向撚帶到架！<br />\n<br />\n最後要重整返啦<br />\n中大今日無輸到 <br />\n只係戰略要調整<br />\n保住條命先會做到持續抗爭<br />\n加上唔要命都唔係咁呀？<br />\n<br />\n再重要啲係<br />\n見到分化post<br />\n無理互屌<br />\n真係可以skip<br />\n大家比心機<br />\n<br />\n黎明會來<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0160ba68506d5342c26b3093795acfc197179c2f","tid":1725112,"uid":87582,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T16:02:18.000Z","msg":"自己推"},{"pid":"df1bd04f08d94f9292824cc0b80327e818d6f6df","tid":1725112,"uid":87582,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T16:03:38.000Z","msg":"自己推"},{"pid":"a86120fa227406ece2af30a960420093c70f445a","tid":1725112,"uid":87582,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T16:07:38.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"c9b9ffa58428281770ab54a5738d7abacc033884","tid":1725112,"uid":87582,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T16:58:06.000Z","msg":"再推"},{"pid":"ad8ccc427abea86e082d6b0e306badf1468497bb","tid":1725112,"uid":293841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T16:59:09.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"973a8346b356068acf9b5a1b3d677a5b55f9e64b","tid":1725112,"uid":218731,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T16:59:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" 